{"ja490:0.1":"Jataka ","ja490:0.2":"Pakinnakanipata ","ja490:0.3":"Salikedaravagga ","ja490:0.4":"7. Pancuposathikajataka ","ja490:1.1":"“Appossukko dani tuvam kapota, ","ja490:1.2":"Vihangama na tava bhojanattho; ","ja490:1.3":"Khudam pipasam adhivasayanto, ","ja490:1.4":"Kasma bhavamposathiko kapota”. ","ja490:2.1":"“Aham pure giddhigato kapotiya, ","ja490:2.2":"Asmim padesasmimubho ramama; ","ja490:2.3":"Athaggahi sakuniko kapotim, ","ja490:2.4":"Akamako taya vina ahosim. ","ja490:3.1":"Nanabhava vippayogena tassa, ","ja490:3.2":"Manomayam vedana vedayami; ","ja490:3.3":"Tasma ahamposatham palayami, ","ja490:3.4":"Rago mamam ma punaragamasi”. ","ja490:4.1":"“Anujjugami uraga dujivha, ","ja490:4.2":"Dathavudho ghoravisosi sappa; ","ja490:4.3":"Khudam pipasam adhivasayanto, ","ja490:4.4":"Kasma bhavamposathiko nu digha. ","ja490:5.1":"Usabho ahu balava gamikassa, ","ja490:5.2":"Calakkaku vannabalupapanno; ","ja490:5.3":"So mam akkami tam kupito adamsim, ","ja490:5.4":"Dukkhabhitunno maranam upaga. ","ja490:6.1":"Tato jana nikkhamitvana gama, ","ja490:6.2":"Kanditva roditva apakkamimsu; ","ja490:6.3":"Tasma ahamposatham palayami, ","ja490:6.4":"Kodho mamam ma punaragamasi. ","ja490:7.1":"Matana mamsani bahu susane, ","ja490:7.2":"Manunnarupam tava bhojane tam; ","ja490:7.3":"Khudam pipasam adhivasayanto, ","ja490:7.4":"Kasma bhavamposathiko singala. ","ja490:8.1":"Pavisi kucchim mahato gajassa, ","ja490:8.2":"Kunape rato hatthimamsesu giddho; ","ja490:8.3":"Unho ca vato tikhina ca rasmiyo, ","ja490:8.4":"Te sosayum tassa karisamaggam. ","ja490:9.1":"Kiso ca pandu ca aham bhadante, ","ja490:9.2":"Na me ahu nikkhamanaya maggo; ","ja490:9.3":"Maha ca megho sahasa pavassi, ","ja490:9.4":"So temayi tassa karisamaggam. ","ja490:10.1":"Tato aham nikkhamisam bhadante, ","ja490:10.2":"Cando yatha rahumukha pamutto; ","ja490:10.3":"Tasma ahamposatham palayami, ","ja490:10.4":"Lobho mamam ma punaragamasi. ","ja490:11.1":"Vammikathupasmim kipillikani, ","ja490:11.2":"Nippothayanto tuvam pure carasi; ","ja490:11.3":"Khudam pipasam adhivasayanto, ","ja490:11.4":"Kasma bhavamposathiko nu accha. ","ja490:12.1":"Sakam niketam atihilayano, ","ja490:12.2":"Atricchata mallagamam agacchim; ","ja490:12.3":"Tato jana nikkhamitvana gama, ","ja490:12.4":"Kodandakena paripothayimsu mam. ","ja490:13.1":"So bhinnasiso ruhiramakkhitango, ","ja490:13.2":"Paccagamasim sakam niketam; ","ja490:13.3":"Tasma ahamposatham palayami, ","ja490:13.4":"Atricchata ma punaragamasi”. ","ja490:14.1":"“Yam no apucchittha tuvam bhadante, ","ja490:14.2":"Sabbeva byakarimha yathapajanam; ","ja490:14.3":"Mayampi pucchama tuvam bhadante, ","ja490:14.4":"Kasma bhavamposathiko nu brahme”. ","ja490:15.1":"“Anupalitto mama assamamhi, ","ja490:15.2":"Paccekabuddho muhuttam nisidi; ","ja490:15.3":"So mam avedi gatimagatinca, ","ja490:15.4":"Namanca gottam carananca sabbam. ","ja490:16.1":"Evampaham vandi na tassa pade, ","ja490:16.2":"Na capi nam managatena pucchim; ","ja490:16.3":"Tasma ahamposatham palayami, ","ja490:16.4":"Mano mamam ma punaragamasi”ti. ","ja490:17.1":"Pancuposathikajatakam sattamam. "}